latestPosts.caption:
It’s one year since I moved to India and I do love this country with all my heart! ❤️

But if you ask me if I miss Russia, I would definitely say “yes”. I do miss my hometown Ulyanovsk and all my family and friends there!

So this reel is a small reminder to myself “don’t forget your roots” 🙏🏼
